220 Greetings
EHLO
250-Hello there
250-PIPELINING
250 CHUNKING
MAIL FROM
RCPT TO
BDAT 344 LAST
*data 344
450 greylisted mail-from
550 rcpt ungood lacking mail-from
500 bdat ungood lacking mail-from
QUIT
225 OK
****
